# Iceberg 与 Spark 集成

Iceberg为Apache Spark提供了深度集成，支持多个Spark版本（v3.3、v3.4、v3.5）。Spark是最常用的Iceberg查询引擎之一。

## 核心组件

### Spark Catalog

- [SparkCatalog](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/SparkCatalog.java): Spark目录的Iceberg实现
- [SparkSessionCatalog](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/SparkSessionCatalog.java): Spark会话目录的实现

### 数据源

- [SparkTable](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/source/SparkTable.java): Spark表的Iceberg实现
- [SparkBatchQueryScan](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/source/SparkBatchQueryScan.java): Spark批量查询扫描
- [SparkMicroBatchStream](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/source/SparkMicroBatchStream.java): Spark微批流处理支持

### 读写支持

- [SparkBatchWrite](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/source/SparkBatchWrite.java): Spark批量写入支持
- [SparkMicroBatchWrite](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/source/SparkMicroBatchWrite.java): Spark微批写入支持

### 格式转换

- [SparkTypeToType](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/SparkTypeToType.java): 在Spark类型和Iceberg类型之间转换
- [SparkValueConverter](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/data/SparkValueConverter.java): 在Spark值和Iceberg值之间转换

## Spark SQL扩展

- [IcebergSpark](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/spark/Spark3Util.java): Spark SQL支持工具
- [SparkExtensions](mdc:spark/v3.5/spark-extensions/src/main/scala/org/apache/iceberg/spark/extensions/IcebergSparkSessionExtensions.scala): Spark会话扩展，添加Iceberg特定的SQL命令

### 支持的SQL命令

- `ALTER TABLE ... ADD PARTITION FIELD`: 添加分区字段
- `ALTER TABLE ... DROP PARTITION FIELD`: 删除分区字段
- `ALTER TABLE ... WRITE ORDERED BY`: 设置排序顺序
- `CALL system.rollback_to_snapshot`: 回滚到特定快照
- `CALL system.set_current_snapshot`: 设置当前快照
- `MERGE INTO`: 支持高效的更新和插入操作

## 时间旅行支持

Iceberg允许Spark查询访问表的历史版本：

```sql
-- 按时间戳查询
SELECT * FROM my_table TIMESTAMP AS OF '2023-01-01 12:00:00'

-- 按快照ID查询
SELECT * FROM my_table VERSION AS OF 123456
```

## 常见使用模式

### 批处理读写

```scala
// 读取Iceberg表
val df = spark.read.format("iceberg").load("catalog.db.table")

// 写入Iceberg表
df.write
  .format("iceberg")
  .mode("append")
  .save("catalog.db.table")
```

### 流式处理

```scala
// 流式读取
val stream = spark.readStream
  .format("iceberg")
  .load("catalog.db.table")

// 流式写入
df.writeStream
  .format("iceberg")
  .outputMode("append")
  .option("checkpointLocation", "/path/to/checkpoint")
  .start("catalog.db.table")
```

### 高级功能

```scala
// 元数据表查询
val files = spark.read.format("iceberg").load("catalog.db.table.files")
val snapshots = spark.read.format("iceberg").load("catalog.db.table.snapshots")

// 谓词下推和分区裁剪
val filteredDF = spark.read.format("iceberg")
  .load("catalog.db.table")
  .filter($"date" > "2023-01-01" && $"id" === 123)
```
